351
00:26:03,140 --> 00:26:05,698
Ma'am, I set the system's ID.

352
00:26:05,698 --> 00:26:06,939
Only my phone can have a signal.

353
00:26:06,939 --> 00:26:09,119
Give it here.
[Du Long Xuan]

354
00:26:12,240 --> 00:26:13,880
