504
00:35:04,659 --> 00:35:05,940
Don't you need some rest?

505
00:35:05,940 --> 00:35:08,879
Do you think everyone is as idle as you?

506
00:35:08,879 --> 00:35:10,880
You...

507
00:35:11,760 --> 00:35:14,259
Forget it.

